natural_language_question: Who is the founder of Penguin Books?

PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> SELECT DISTINCT ?founder WHERE { ?resource rdf:type dbo:Company ; dbo:founder ?founder .
